data.description: Amazing chance in the highly sought-after Morningside Park - Inglewood neighborhood! This property features two spacious units, perfectly situated on a wide, peaceful street just a few blocks away from Circle Park. The duplex comprises two 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom units, each with its own laundry room and separate utilities/meters. The backyard is large and there are two 1-car garages located at the rear that would be a great ADU opportunity to generate even more rental income!    The location is incredibly convenient, being in close proximity to SoFi Stadium, the Forum, the proposed site for the Clippers Arena, and LAX. Additionally, the area is experiencing rapid development, with a new train/metro line connecting Inglewood to LAX, as well as numerous infrastructure investments in preparation for the 2028 Olympics. Exciting developments such as new shopping plazas, retail outlets, fine dining establishments, and entertainment venues are being established nearby.    The units have been meticulously maintained, are move-in ready, and boast desirable features like dual pane windows, updated heating, newer A/C, and the possibility of refinished oak hardwood flooring beneath the carpet. This is an exceptional investment opportunity in an area that is continuously improving, leading to increased property values. Please respect the privacy of the tenants and refrain from disturbing them.
